# Rust build output — the lint gate's cargo leg (LNT01, ADR-0037) generates a
# large `target/` at the repo root of any Rust crate it checks; keep those build
# artifacts out of the index so a `git add -A` never sweeps them in.
target/

# Local padz note store (out of source control)
.padz/

# Agent worktrees (isolation: worktree) — never tracked
.claude/worktrees/
.todos.db
